        System.out.println("There are a lot of rules within this game:");
        System.out.println("1) there are 26 cases in total - each case holds money in it. however this is unknown to you. ");
        System.out.println("2) pick any of the 26 cases - the case you chose will be kept until the very end of the game");
        System.out.println("3) after, you will open other cases to reveal the number value ");
        System.out.println("4) after a few cases are opened, the banker offers you money to stop playing");
        System.out.println("5) you have the option to stop playing & take the deal, or to keep playing");
        System.out.println("6) at the end, you can choose to keep your case or switch to the last one.");
